            <Text fill="#ff7f00" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="The artifact collection in the Grand Egyptian Museum (GEM) is one of the most comprehensive and significant in the world, dedicated exclusively to the artifacts of ancient Egypt. With over 100,000 pieces, the museum’s collection spans the entirety of ancient Egyptian history, from the Prehistoric Period through the Greco-Roman era, showcasing the rich and diverse heritage of this ancient civilization." wrappingWidth="820.13671875">
