            <Text fill="#ff7f00" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="The GEM’s collection is not just about displaying artifacts; it also serves as an educational resource. The museum provides detailed information and context for each item, helping visitors to understand the significance of what they are seeing. Through these artifacts, the GEM offers a comprehensive view of ancient Egyptian civilization, its achievements, and its lasting legacy." wrappingWidth="743.13671875">
